author: Simon Carswell
title: Coronavirus: Ten more deaths reported in Republic
description: Citywest hotel and conference centre now a facility ready to accept patients who cannot self-isolate at home
content:
A further 10 people have died as a result of coronavirus, bringing the death toll from the disease in the Republic to 46.
Eight men and two women died from Covid-19, according to the latest figures released by the States National Public Health Emergency Team… [+6679 chars]
